title: Hyenas
body:
Prompt: “I regret a lot of things. Having this conversation tops the list.”

Request: yes | no

Paring: Loki x fem!reader 

Warning: none; uhh a little bit of swearing?

Word count: 493

This is my first time writing a while snsns so please don’t kill me. - Lix.

As Natasha, Tony, Thor, and Wanda entered the common area, they were surprised to see the two lovebirds in a full-blown fight in the middle of the living room.

“Loki! For the last time, it wasn’t me!” Y/N shouted once again. She ran her hand through her messy locks, trying to comb out her own frustration.

Loki wasn’t any better as he rolled his eyes, turning away from the agitated girl.

“Is… everything alright here?” Wanda asked tentatively, fighting the urge to sneak into their minds.

“Wanda!” Y/N jerked her head towards her friend’s voice, eyes lighting up as she saw the group entering the room. “You’re all here! Great, now please tell Loki that this is stupid and we shouldn’t even be fighting about this.” Y/N looked at her friends almost pleadingly.

“Oh please Y/N, you’re the one who had absolutely no regrets after what you’ve done.”

“Because it wasn’t me! And for the record, I regret a lot of things, Loki. Having this conversation tops the fucking list.”

While everyone was trying to stifle their laughter, Natasha had the decency to ask what exactly got the two in such a heated discussion. Though, the small smile on her face gave out that she was having fun with this.

“My beloved Y/N here decided that it was a good idea to finish my pot of coffee.” Anger and annoyance clear in his voice.

The rest couldn’t help but burst into laughter, even the black widow herself gave up fighting.

“Loki, I swear on Odin’s grave that I didn’t.”

“Wait, wait, wait. Let me get this straight. You two were, are, having a full blown fight, over a pot of coffee?” Tony was practically on the floor and it was a miracle that he got that sentence out without much trouble.

“I was ACCUSED!” Y/N shouted, cleared offended by Tony and the rest of the laughing gang.

“Lady Y/N, my apologies but this is just hilarious.” Thor laughed as he gripped Y/N’s shoulder gently.

“Ugh, you four hyenas are no help.” Y/N groaned in frustration as she flops down on the couch.

Just when everyone is about to die from laughter, the Captain walked in.

“What are you guys laughing about?” He asked as he proceeds to take sips from his mug.

Everyone stopped and turned their attention to Steve and no one talked for a split second.

“Steve, what’s in your cup?” Tony asked while trying to hide another building up laughter.

“Coffee. There was some left in the pot earlier today. Why?”

His face was painted with confusion as he watched his crew burst into laughter once again and both Loki and Y/N had a huge blush that spread across their faces.

“You owe me one Rogers.” Y/N mumbled as she walked passed Steve, trying to escape the embarrassment, leaving behind a very confused Captain and a group of laughing hyenas.

blog.title: L'Echappée Belle d' Ygraïn
blog.description:
" Elle voulait une vie d'aventures, une vie folle, une vie plus grande qu'elle.Et l'on disait tout autour d'elle : [Ygraïn] rêve". Timothée de Fombelle, Victoria rêve

Je ne sais pas dessiner, les artworks que vous verrez ici ne sont pas les miens. Mais vous trouverez toujours un lien vers une gallerie de leurs auteurs. Personnellement, je ne fais que des montages (wallpaper, digiscrap, bannière ...) à partir de captures d'écran (screencap).. Ce tumblr est ma gallerie de rêves éphémères, mon échappée belle où je viens me ressourcer, me changer les idées, trouver un support à mes rêveries grâce aux fabuleux arts de d'autres artistes. .
Pour me contacter, en cas de problème: ygrain@gmail.com

Sinon: mon blog de lecture est: https://les-lectures-d-ygrain.tumblr.com/
